                      class="instruction"
                    >
                      <div>
                        <span
                          class="instruction-number"
                        >
                          1
                        </span>
                      </div>
                      <div
                        class="instruction-text"
                      >
                        Go under 
                        <b>
                          Themes
                        </b>
                         in your Online Store and click on
                         
                        <b>
                          Customize
                        </b>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="instruction"
                    >
                      <div>
                        <span
                          class="instruction-number"
                        >
                          2
                        </span>
                      </div>
                      <div
                        class="instruction-text"
                      >
                        Then under 
                        <b>
                          Theme actions
                        </b>
                        , click on 
                        <b>
                          Edit Code
                        </b>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="instruction"
                    >
                      <div>
                        <span
                          class="instruction-number"
                        >
                          3
                        </span>
                      </div>
                      <div
                        class="instruction-text"
                      >
                        Open file 
                        <b>
                          theme.liquid
                        </b>
                         and scroll down to the bottom
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="instruction"
                    >
                      <div>
                        <span
                          class="instruction-number"
                        >
                          4
                        </span>
                      </div>
                      <div
                        class="instruction-text"
                      >
                        Finally, copy the code below and paste it above the
                         
                        <b>
                          &lt;/body&gt;
                        </b>
                         tag
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="alert warning"
                    >
                      <div
                        class="content"
                      >
                        <span
                          class="label"
                        >
                          Please note that by copying the code to your Shopify
                           
                          <b>
                            theme.liquid
                          </b>
                           files, the chat will also be shown on all webpages. Make sure to copy the code to just specific pages if needed.
                        </span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
